2096
01:51:25,671 --> 01:51:26,671
Somehow, he found his way back to Belsize
Park.

2097
01:51:26,671 --> 01:51:27,671
But outside his front door, he realized that
he couldn't get into the flat without his

2098
01:51:27,671 --> 01:51:28,671
keys.

