01:51:29,671 --> 01:51:30,671
Sylvie found him unconscious there in the
morning when she brought Jasmine for a visit.

2101
01:51:30,671 --> 01:51:31,671
Sylvie had ended her relationship with Callum
O'Neill and Dexter now got on quite well with

2102
01:51:31,671 --> 01:51:32,671
his ex-wife.

2103
01:51:32,671 --> 01:51:33,671
When she found Dexter outside his door, she
phoned his father.

2104
01:51:33,671 --> 01:51:34,671
She had her own keys, so she took Dexter into
the flat and washed him and found him some

2105
01:51:34,671 --> 01:51:35,671
clean clothes.

2106
01:51:35,671 --> 01:51:36,671
Later, Stephen Mayhew arrived and took Dexter
back to Oxfordshire.

2107
01:51:36,671 --> 01:51:37,671
Now that they had both lost their wives, they
understood each other better.

2108
01:51:37,671 --> 01:51:38,671
Dexter's father was gentle with him.

