On the third anniversary of Emma's death,
Dexter was in Edinburgh, with Maddy and Jasmine.

2157
01:52:26,671 --> 01:52:27,671
Dexter and Maddy were a couple now and they
were having a short holiday with Dexter's

2158
01:52:27,671 --> 01:52:28,671
daughter.

