2206
01:53:15,671 --> 01:53:16,671
Tilly said.

2207
01:53:16,671 --> 01:53:17,671
'You can be romantic there.'

2208
01:53:17,671 --> 01:53:18,671
So after breakfast, Emma and Dexter went out
into the city.

2209
01:53:18,671 --> 01:53:19,671
Emma took her camera with her and they bought
food for a picnic.

2210
01:53:19,671 --> 01:53:20,671
Dexter was worried about climbing Arthur's
